My English Diary is a two level series of early writing books that are designed in a diary format. This series aims to help students improve their English through the skill of diary writing. Through each diary entry, students gradually become familiar with various formats from simple and easy entries to challenging entries. The events discussed in the sample diary entries span the four seasons of a year introducing students to many different enjoyable topics. By studying with My English Diary book 1 and 2, students will grow in confidence as they express their thoughts in English.In the format of a picture diaryEasy-to-follow lesson flowFun and engaging material for diary entriesIlluminating illustrationsPractice using the target verbs
